SphereMakerMaker Scene Graph Generator Plug-in
==============================================

The SphereMakerMaker Scene Graph Generator (SGG) plug-in is an example of a
recursive SGG plug-in. It uses several SphereMaker plug-ins (see the GeoMakers
plug-ins) to generate several sets of spheres.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/SphereMakerMaker.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a Katana
   resources path.
